        "de158e68-5d0d-4819-a625-e2dabdff87d1": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Key Benefits",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p><strong>Reduces Chest Wrinkles & Fine Lines </strong>- Helps smooth out visible chest wrinkles, creases, and sleep lines by keeping the skin gently stretched and flat during rest.</p><p><strong>Wrinkle Smoothing</strong> – Helps reduce the depth and appearance of fine lines and creases across the neck and décolleté.</p><p><strong>Boosts Skin Hydration</strong> – Medical-grade silicone creates an occlusive barrier that locks in moisture, plumps the skin, and improves overall texture.</p><p><strong>Prevents New Wrinkle Formation</strong> – By preventing skin folding while you sleep, it helps stop new chest wrinkles from forming over time—especially for side sleepers.</p><p><strong>Supports Collagen Production – </strong>Medical-grade silicone helps retain moisture and flatten lines.</p><p><strong>Comfortable & Non-Invasive</strong> - Soft, flexible, and gentle on the skin—designed for overnight use without irritation or discomfort. No needles, no downtime.</p><p><strong>Clinically Tested and Dermatologist Approved – Safe for sensitive skin and proven to deliver visible results.</strong></p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_QnkEdx": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How does it work?",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>You can use the <strong>Chest Wrinkle Patch</strong> daily, either in the evening or overnight, as part of your skincare routine. <br/><br/>Simply apply the patch to clean, dry skin on your chest and leave it on for the recommended time to let the medical-grade silicone work its magic. <br/><br/>For best results, use it consistently—apply after cleansing and before bedtime as the final step in your evening routine. Wake up to smoother, more hydrated skin with each use.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_WYG8GJ": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I use it for sensitive skin?",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Yes! All skin types, including sensitive skin.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_kwzWVt": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Ingredients",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>We do not include any harmful parabens or other nasties. We also NEVER test on animals.<br/><strong><br/>Medical-grade silicone</strong> is a high-quality, biocompatible material widely used in skincare and medical applications. It’s safe, non-toxic, and gentle on sensitive skin.<br/><br/><strong>How it helps with neck wrinkles:</strong></p><ul><li>Creates a breathable barrier that hydrates and plumps skin, softening wrinkles.<br/></li><li>Maintains moisture to boost collagen and improve elasticity over time.<br/></li><li>Molds to the neck, reducing crease depth and preventing new lines.<br/></li><li>Durable for multiple uses, making it cost-effective and sustainable.<br/></li><li>Hypoallergenic and non-irritating, suitable for sensitive skin.</li></ul>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_QGc8Kr": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Shipping & Delivery",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p><strong>Processing Time:</strong><br/>Once your order is placed, please allow 24 hours for us to process and prepare your order for shipment.<br/><br/><strong>Shipping Time:</strong><br/>After your order is dispatched, it will typically take 4-8 business days to reach you, depending on your location.<br/><br/><strong>Tracking Information:</strong><br/>Once your order has been shipped, you will receive an email containing your tracking number. You can use this to track your package and stay updated on its delivery status.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_8h6X4m": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Return & Exchange Policy",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>We want you to be fully satisfied with your purchase! If you are not completely happy with your order, we accept returns and exchanges within 60 days from the date of purchase.<br/><br/>Contact us via the website or via email: info@niforashop.com</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        }
      },
